✨GIVEAWAY C L O S E D✨Calling all Boston area nurses and CNAs!

Nurse Blake is coming to Boston on his Comedy Tour on October 13th and we want to give you and your nurse bestie a night out!

We’re giving away 2 tickets to the show and dinner on us.

HOW TO ENTER THE GIVEAWAY:

1️⃣ Follow @connectrnapp
2️⃣ Like this post 💜
3️⃣ Tag your nurse bestie that you want to take to Nurse Blake’s show

For a BONUS entry, share this post to your story and tag @connectrnapp

2 lucky nurses will be notified on Tuesday, October 11th at 9 am ET via an update to this post and DM.

Winners must be located in the United States and must be 18 years or older at the time of entry. This contest is not affiliated with Instagram or Facebook. By participating or entering, you agree to release Instagram of all liability.
